--- GOTCHAS ---
1. No dev server. Changes need full build+deploy cycle.
2. recordLogin must complete before reload or logs are lost.
3. FamilyGroupRequestScreen requires !hasFamilyId check BEFORE loading check in useEffect.
4. GoogleLinkScreen does NOT receive googleUid prop (removed — unused). App.tsx closes over googleLinkData.uid directly.
5. PersonNode data cast requires `as unknown as PersonNodeData` due to NodeProps.data typing.
6. Firestore rules: allow read, write: if true — no server-side auth enforcement.
7. FCM push only works when app is installed as PWA. Browser tabs get nothing.
8. Admin email displayed to users comes from admin member's google_email field. If admin hasn't linked Google, field is null.
9. settings/push defaults used in Functions when doc doesn't exist: {sendHourKST:8, offsets:[0,1,3,7], maxChusu:6, enableBirthday:true, enableDeathDay:true}
10. CSS confirm-backdrop/confirm-box etc. defined in App.css globally — not in AdminView.css.

